{"tid":276991,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"23歲醉娃疑遭新上司強姦　庭上哭訴：點解會發生喺我身上","createTime":"2017-06-09T08:56:36.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-09T10:09:05.000Z","uid":2419,"like":0,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"1f029070464e0dc7e7ec2f5d17fe5406b6727042","tid":276991,"uid":2419,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-09T08:56:36.000Z","msg":"23歲女子於2015年5月獲聘為男商人的助理，惟上班數天後在「Happy Friday」到酒吧消遣，她與2名男同事及男上司飲酒到凌晨5時許，被帶到四季酒店，少女醉得要坐輪椅進房。女子與上司在21樓海景房共處一室，酒醒後懷疑被強姦而報警求助。男商人今在高院受審，女子出庭作供時不斷哭泣，<span style=\"color: red;\">「唔知點解呢啲事會發生喺我身上」</span>。<br />\n      <br />\n      被告鄺志榮否認一項企圖強姦罪及非禮罪。<br />\n      <br />\n      事主X供稱，當時23歲，獲聘數天後與同事及被告到銅鑼灣一間酒吧消遣，直到凌晨3男1女坐的士前往四季酒店，但她指不知身在何處，忘記被誰送入房間。醒後發現自己身穿睡袍及內褲，被告睡在身旁，她稱當時很害怕。她一度半醒半醉，再醒時感覺被親吻及摸胸，但全身無力反抗。她不斷哭泣，哭聲漸強，但被告用手摀著口，叫她不要吵。被告又問她：「知唔知我係邊個？點解你喊？」，X表示知道，但被告仍不斷親吻她。其後X推開被告，被告讓她飲水後便倒頭大睡，X乘機逃走。<br />\n      <br />\n      法庭記者：方嘉欣<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.stheadline.com/inews-content.php?cat=a&amp;nid=111349\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.stheadline.com%2Finews-content.php%3Fcat%3Da%26nid%3D111349&d=XkTkS7%2BQljrTulh8xmOTaYzu7PIJYhBZqlGrkalTKs4%3D&h=9639715b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.stheadline.com%2Finews-content.php%3Fcat%3Da%26nid%3D111349&h=c814efb5\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.stheadline.com/inews-content.php?cat=a&amp;nid=111349</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n唔知點解?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b7cd01619eab1d0553b016729aea7a34077d16b0","tid":276991,"uid":22858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-09T08:58:37.000Z","msg":"去得四季 <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"55c8d1faaad8a3f6336c441e969c59ca1e29c65a","tid":276991,"uid":33053,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-09T08:59:50.000Z","msg":"g"},{"pid":"15fd03c52fbb72044510421d8e1a471fa80fdc48","tid":276991,"uid":9315,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-09T09:00:58.000Z","msg":"坦白講除非比人落藥/拎槍指住飲酒<br />\n真係喊都無謂<br />\n<br />\n冇靠得住既朋友一齊仲敢飲到貓曬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9c030a4419aed21766fb4e86ba0511f7cd271cd9","tid":276991,"uid":102132,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-09T09:02:06.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"06dcaf39a70832853e670a1a4ffb351dc9864c8d","tid":276991,"uid":5649,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-09T09:03:24.000Z","msg":"少女醉得要坐輪椅進房<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"946ed3b4fdb346005c23ace09e419a5c9e0cf11f","tid":276991,"uid":28624,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-09T09:18:24.000Z","msg":"臭雞 三唔識七返得果幾日就去呢d地方<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"26b110d0a125cc4671cffb43300a11041de91929","tid":276991,"uid":72457,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-09T09:34:42.000Z","msg":"四季，私鐘啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"57acdefa51b2ca9fc66e044826789fcbe80a570b","tid":276991,"uid":6817,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-09T09:36:57.000Z","msg":"勞資糾紛"},{"pid":"c9b4525891363337796fc7620430b2e9c6734b12","tid":276991,"uid":55043,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-09T09:38:29.000Z","msg":"真心<br />\n<br />\n如冇落藥，係女方不勝酒力然後出事，我提醒女仕們唔好飲咁多，算唔算blame the victim